<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="27Jun1938"><font color="red">27 June 1938</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from Richard de la Mere to Paul L&eacute;on): Thank you for your two letters of June 22nd and June 24th, which arrived almost at the same time, together with Mr Joyce&apos;s corrected galley proofs for episodes 1, 2 and 3 of Part II, his copy for the additional matter at the end of episode 3, and those revised galleys 15a to 17a.  </div>
